# Salesforce gives us alot of tools to send out emails and receive emails with apex code.
<br><br>
In this sections the examples will show how to send out emails via apex and how to set all params. (Single, Multi, CC, BCC)
<br>
Parsing emails coming into an "email service" you setup within Salesforce. (Salesforce creates an email address for you to use as an endpoint of sorts)
